---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { siteBase } from "../lib/site";

const title = "COMPASS: Build Intuition. Trust the Reading.";
const description =
  "A 6-week live programme for tarot, oracle, and Lenormand readers who want to move beyond meanings and learn how to trust the reading.";
const ogUrl = new URL("/compass/", siteBase(Astro)).href;
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} ogUrl={ogUrl} tdcPlacement="none">
  <article class="compass page-inner">
    <section class="compass__hero">
      <div class="compass__hero-copy compass__panel">
        <p class="compass__eyebrow">6-week live programme</p>
        <h1 class="compass__h1">COMPASS: Build Intuition. Trust the Reading.</h1>

        <p class="compass__p">
          You already know the cards. That is not the problem.
        </p>

        <p class="compass__p">
          The problem is what happens when you’re in the middle of a reading. You see something, then hesitate. You feel a clear thread, then second-guess it. You start explaining instead of interpreting. You reach for meanings instead of staying with what is actually unfolding.
        </p>

        <a class="compass__cta compass__cta--primary" href="/compass/apply/">
          Apply for COMPASS
        </a>

        <a class="compass__sub-link" href="/articles/compass-method/">
          Read the COMPASS Method article
        </a>
      </div>

      <figure class="compass__hero-figure compass__panel">
        <img
          src="/images/articles/compass-method/compass-method-hero.png"
          alt="Illustration of the COMPASS Method framework for clear intuitive readings."
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="compass__hero-image"
        />
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class="compass__section compass__section--soft">
      <p class="compass__eyebrow">Problem fit</p>
      <h2 class="compass__h2">If This Sounds Like You</h2>
      <ul class="compass__list compass__list--card">
        <li>You know the meanings, but your readings still feel uncertain</li>
        <li>You start strong, then lose the thread halfway through</li>
        <li>You over-explain instead of saying what you actually see</li>
        <li>You feel intuitive hits, then immediately doubt them</li>
        <li>
          You keep looking for the “right” meaning instead of trusting your read
        </li>
        <li>
          You finish readings and think: that wasn’t as clear as it should have been
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="compass__section">
      <p class="compass__eyebrow">Method</p>
      <h2 class="compass__h2">The COMPASS Method</h2>
      <p class="compass__pillars">
        <span>Center</span>
        <span>Open</span>
        <span>Map</span>
        <span>Perceive</span>
        <span>Align</span>
        <span>Sense</span>
        <span>Seal</span>
      </p>
      <p class="compass__p">
        This is not about learning more tarot. It is about learning how to read.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="compass__section compass__section--soft">
      <p class="compass__eyebrow">Learning outcomes</p>
      <h2 class="compass__h2">What You’ll Learn</h2>
      <p class="compass__p">
        Most tarot training focuses on what the cards mean.
        COMPASS focuses on what the reader is doing.
      </p>
      <ul class="compass__list compass__list--card">
        <li>Trust your own perception in a reading</li>
        <li>Stay with what is actually unfolding</li>
        <li>Communicate what you see clearly and cleanly</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="compass__section">
      <p class="compass__eyebrow">Process</p>
      <h2 class="compass__h2">How It Works</h2>
      <p class="compass__p compass__process-intro">
        This is a 6-week live programme for a small group of readers.
      </p>
      <ul class="compass__list compass__list--card">
        <li>Weekly live sessions</li>
        <li>Guided practice readings</li>
        <li>Direct feedback and correction</li>
        <li>Real application, not theory</li>
      </ul>

      <a class="compass__cta compass__cta--secondary" href="/compass/apply/">
        Apply for COMPASS
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="compass__section compass__section--warm">
      <p class="compass__eyebrow">Authority</p>
      <h2 class="compass__h2">About Leigh Spencer</h2>
      <p class="compass__p">
        I’ve been reading tarot and oracle cards for over 40 years.
        Before that, I spent 30 years as a journalist, broadcaster, and editor, trained to observe, interpret, and communicate clearly.
      </p>
      <p class="compass__p">
        COMPASS is built from real reading experience, and from seeing exactly where readers lose trust in themselves.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="compass__section">
      <p class="compass__eyebrow">Programme details</p>
      <h2 class="compass__h2">Enrollment</h2>
      <ul class="compass__list">
        <li>Limited to 6 participants</li>
        <li>Minimum 2 participants to run</li>
        <li>Live only, not replay-based delivery</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="compass__p">
        You are asked to apply because fit matters.
      </p>
      <p class="compass__p">
        This is a small live programme where direct feedback and outcome matter more than filling places.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="compass__section">
      <p class="compass__eyebrow">Investment</p>
      <h2 class="compass__h2">Investment</h2>
      <p class="compass__p">
        USD $197
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="compass__section compass__section--final">
      <p class="compass__eyebrow">Apply</p>
      <h2 class="compass__h2">Apply</h2>
      <p class="compass__p">
        Send a short message with:
      </p>
      <ul class="compass__list">
        <li>Your experience level</li>
        <li>What’s not working in your readings</li>
        <li>Why you want to join</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="compass__p">
        If accepted, your place will be held for 48 hours.
      </p>
      <a class="compass__cta" href="/compass/apply/">Apply Now</a>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .compass {
    padding: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    max-width: 62rem;
  }

  .compass__hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .compass__hero-copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .compass__panel {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--paper) 0%, rgba(216, 219, 241, 0.24) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(198, 161, 74, 0.35);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    padding: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
  }

  .compass__hero-figure {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .compass__hero-image {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 0.2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(198, 161, 74, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(13, 50, 77, 0.12);
  }

  .compass__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-nav);
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .compass__h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 2.65rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--mountain-water);
  }

  .compass__h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.8vw, 1.65rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--mountain-water);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .compass__section + .compass__section {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .compass__p {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    line-height: 1.72;
  }

  .compass__pillars {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .compass__pillars span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.42rem 0.68rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(116, 179, 206, 0.45);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(116, 179, 206, 0.1);
    font-family: var(--font-nav);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mountain-water);
  }

  .compass__list {
    margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
    padding-left: 1.35rem;
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .compass__list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .compass__list--card {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem 0.45rem 2.1rem;
    background: var(--shore);
    border: 1px solid rgba(198, 161, 74, 0.3);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }

  .compass__process-intro {
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .compass__section {
    padding: clamp(1.1rem, 2.6vw, 1.45rem);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
  }

  .compass__section--soft {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(216, 219, 241, 0.22) 0%, rgba(243, 240, 234, 0.9) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(116, 179, 206, 0.25);
  }

  .compass__section--warm {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(198, 161, 74, 0.12) 0%, rgba(243, 240, 234, 0.95) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(198, 161, 74, 0.3);
  }

  .compass__section--final {
    background: var(--near-black);
    border: 1px solid rgba(198, 161, 74, 0.45);
  }

  .compass__section--final .compass__h2,
  .compass__section--final .compass__p,
  .compass__section--final .compass__list {
    color: var(--paper);
  }

  .compass__section--final .compass__eyebrow {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .compass__section--final .compass__cta {
    color: var(--paper);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }

  .compass__sub-link {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-nav);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--mountain-water);
  }

  .compass__sub-link:hover {
    color: var(--sky);
  }

  .compass__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-nav);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--mountain-water);
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .compass__cta--primary {
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .compass__cta--secondary {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .compass__cta:hover {
    background: rgba(198, 161, 74, 0.14);
    color: var(--mountain-water);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }

  .compass__section--final .compass__cta:hover {
    color: var(--paper);
    background: rgba(198, 161, 74, 0.2);
  }

  .compass__cta:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--gold);
    outline-offset: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .compass__hero {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    }

    .compass__hero-figure {
      order: -1;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .compass__section {
      padding: 0.95rem;
    }

    .compass__h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 9vw, 2.45rem);
    }
  }
</style>

